### Answers to multiplication problems

### $-7 \cdot \frac{3}{49} = -\frac{3}{7}$.
### $-\frac{5}{9} \cdot -\frac{3}{15} = \frac{1}{9}$.

---

### Answers to division problems

### $-\frac{5}{6} \div \frac{3}{4} = -\frac{10}{9}$.
### $-4 \div -\frac{1}{2} = 8$.

